Room.Name: Golden Dolphin Way
Room.ShortDescription: You are walking along Golden Dolphin Way, south of the Golden Dolphin Inn.
Room.LongDescription: The Golden Dolphin Inn is directly to the north. You can see through some of the windows to see that it is a modestly priced inn with just moderate quality service. Although well kept, it lacks some of the glitter and money that some of the other, fancier inns have, such as the Dragon's Tooth Inn.
